[{"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_large.png?m=1650127314", "name": "beijing", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_normal.png?m=1650127314", "title": "北京", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/beijing", "topics": 3695, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Beijing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_mini.png?m=1650127314", "stars": 2115, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 19, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 102175, "username": "magic3584", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/magic3584", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9bee/a327/102175_mini.png?m=1676432172", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9bee/a327/102175_normal.png?m=1676432172", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/9bee/a327/102175_large.png?m=1676432172", "created": 1425387702, "last_modified": 1676432172}, "last_reply_by": "jqtmviyu", "last_touched": 1679498543, "title": "北京开始查电动车过马路不下车推行的行为了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926079", "created": 1679450662, "deleted": 0, "content": "早上送孩子去幼儿园，在斑马线停车等候的时候，一协管员过来跟我说要下车推行，我就问了句“为什么要下车推”，结果人家直接就走了。。。我本意是想让他告诉我为什么\r\n\r\n马路对面有个拖车，上面已经停了两辆电动车，对面俩交警，周围围了 2.3 个骑电动车的\r\n\r\n送完上学回家的时候，转到对面马路靠右行驶避开了交警\r\n\r\n在地铁里查了下\r\n《中华人民共和国道路交通安全法实施条例》第七十条：\r\n\r\n第七十条　驾驶自行车、电动自行车、三轮车在路段上横过机动车道，应当下车推行，有人行横道或者行人过街设施的，应当从人行横道或者行人过街设施通过；没有人行横道、没有行人过街设施或者不便使用行人过街设施的，在确认安全后直行通过。\r\n\r\nhttps://www.sohu.com/a/427482559_492585\r\nhttp://www.gov.cn/banshi/2005-08/23/content_25579_2.htm\r\n\r\n不知道会如何处罚，得注意点了", "content_rendered": "<p>早上送孩子去幼儿园，在斑马线停车等候的时候，一协管员过来跟我说要下车推行，我就问了句“为什么要下车推”，结果人家直接就走了。。。我本意是想让他告诉我为什么</p>\n<p>马路对面有个拖车，上面已经停了两辆电动车，对面俩交警，周围围了 2.3 个骑电动车的</p>\n<p>送完上学回家的时候，转到对面马路靠右行驶避开了交警</p>\n<p>在地铁里查了下\n《中华人民共和国道路交通安全法实施条例》第七十条：</p>\n<p>第七十条　驾驶自行车、电动自行车、三轮车在路段上横过机动车道，应当下车推行，有人行横道或者行人过街设施的，应当从人行横道或者行人过街设施通过；没有人行横道、没有行人过街设施或者不便使用行人过街设施的，在确认安全后直行通过。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.sohu.com/a/427482559_492585\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.sohu.com/a/427482559_492585</a>\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/banshi/2005-08/23/content_25579_2.htm\" rel=\"nofollow\">http://www.gov.cn/banshi/2005-08/23/content_25579_2.htm</a></p>\n<p>不知道会如何处罚，得注意点了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1679450662, "replies": 195, "id": 926079}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_large.png?m=1650127314", "name": "beijing", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_normal.png?m=1650127314", "title": "北京", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/beijing", "topics": 3695, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Beijing", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/1f0e/3dad/19_mini.png?m=1650127314", "stars": 2115, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 19, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 490261, "username": "atkd", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/atkd", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "联系方式：我id加@qq.com", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9ad/6efd/490261_mini.png?m=1679385386", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9ad/6efd/490261_normal.png?m=1679385386", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9ad/6efd/490261_large.png?m=1679385386", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9ad/6efd/490261_xlarge.png?m=1679385386", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9ad/6efd/490261_xlarge.png?m=1679385386", "avatar_xxxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a9ad/6efd/490261_xlarge.png?m=1679385386", "created": 1589849276, "last_modified": 1679385386}, "last_reply_by": "Infinite2K", "last_touched": 1679517160, "title": "北京已达严重污染！扬沙+雾霾天气，简直了。南方人体验过吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926060", "created": 1679448094, "deleted": 0, "content": "https://i.imgur.com/r2kUhHE.jpg\r\n\r\n图片出处： http://news.hsw.cn/system/2023/0322/1603494.shtml\r\n\r\n\r\n过阵子又是柳絮天，南方人体验过吗？", "content_rendered": "<a target=\"_blank\" hr