1679457390, "replies": 110, "id": 926133}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 199957, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3746, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 285020, "username": "forsky", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/forsky", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8e19/cf03/285020_mini.png?m=1579233169", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8e19/cf03/285020_normal.png?m=1579233169", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8e19/cf03/285020_large.png?m=1579233169", "created": 1516521186, "last_modified": 1579233169}, "last_reply_by": "klo424", "last_touched": 1679531555, "title": "Thinkpad 已经这么不耐用了吗？才两年就要爆费？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926050", "created": 1679446081, "deleted": 0, "content": "买来才两年多。\r\n平时用的很爱惜， 昨天用的时候忘记插电源。\r\n系统突然提示电压过低，才想起了没插电。\r\n于是插上电两秒钟后就黑屏了。 \r\n但开机键上的灯和充电指示灯是工作的。 我想着可能没电了，就充电没管。 下午看电充满了， 还是不行。\r\n开机后，黑屏， 但是灯都正常。长按能关机。\r\n拆开 D 面，去除电池后，插电能听到很短的通电的声音。但是风扇不转。。\r\n插拔电源内存硬盘均无效。\r\n\r\n\r\n找到用了两年啊😯。", "content_rendered": "<p>买来才两年多。\n平时用的很爱惜， 昨天用的时候忘记插电源。\n系统突然提示电压过低，才想起了没插电。\n于是插上电两秒钟后就黑屏了。\n但开机键上的灯和充电指示灯是工作的。 我想着可能没电了，就充电没管。 下午看电充满了， 还是不行。\n开机后，黑屏， 但是灯都正常。长按能关机。\n拆开 D 面，去除电池后，插电能听到很短的通电的声音。但是风扇不转。。\n插拔电源内存硬盘均无效。</p>\n<p>找到用了两年啊😯。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1679446081, "replies": 97, "id": 926050}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1677911181", "name": "programmer", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1677911181", "title": "程序员", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer", "topics": 54512, "footer": "", "header": "While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.", "title_alternative": "Programmer", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1677911181", "stars": 8286, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 300, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 14067, "username": "xiaotianhu", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaotianhu", "website": "https://pipebox.pro", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "pipebox.pro 开发中。", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f4cf/ab79/14067_mini.png?m=1668072736", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f4cf/ab79/14067_normal.png?m=1668072736", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f4cf/ab79/14067_large.png?m=1668072736", "created": 1322490463, "last_modified": 1668072736}, "last_reply_by": "herozzm", "last_touched": 1679488232, "title": "各位用 copilot 写代码的小伙伴不会觉得这个剥夺了写代码的乐趣吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926065", "created": 1679449211, "deleted": 0, "content": "先声明下，我不是反对 AIGC ，chatGPT 几乎每天都用 取代了一半搜索引擎的使用，拿来学习简直神器 特别高效。\r\n\r\n但是 copilot 和类似基于 gpt 写代码的产品基本上就没用。\r\n\r\n总觉得这玩意剥夺了写代码的乐趣，让整个工作中唯一能有点乐趣的事儿变的更无趣了。\r\n\r\n我倒是更期待 AI 能自动化测试 比如根据接口文档，或者自然语言文档 就能自己测试了，那就完美了。", "content_rendered": "先声明下，我不是反对 AIGC ，chatGPT 几乎每天都用 取代了一半搜索引擎的使用，拿来学习简直神器 特别高效。<br /><br />但是 copilot 和类似基于 gpt 写代码的产品基本上就没用。<br /><br />总觉得这玩意剥夺了写代码的乐趣，让整个工作中唯一能有点乐趣的事儿变的更无趣了。<br /><br />我倒是更期待 AI 能自动化测试 比如根据接口文档，或者自然语言文档 就能自己测试了，那就完美了。", "last_modified": 1679449211, "replies": 75, "id": 926065}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3dc4/876f/513_large.png?m=1635832578", "name": "markdown", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3dc4/876f/513_normal.png?m=1635832578", "title": "Markdown", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/markdown", "topics": 510, "footer": "", "header": "Markdown is a text-to-HTML conversion tool for web writers.", "title_alternative": "Markdown", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3dc4/876f/513_mini.png?m=1635832578", "stars": 1216, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 513, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 570553, "username": "gangster", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/gangster", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9dc5c2278e609b09b4b5e98449cd04fc?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9dc5c2278e609b09b4b5e98449cd04fc?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/9dc5c2278e609b09b4b5e98449cd04fc?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1643423685, "last_modified": 1665744453}, "last_reply_by": "businessch", "last_touched": 1679526716, "title": "markdown 语法-插入图片", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/926148", "created": 1679459785, "deleted": 0, "content": "### 刚刚学习了 markdown 的图片语法\r\n#### 关联记忆法：将 Markdown 语法与已知概念进行关联。例如，在 Markdown 语法中，感叹号 (!) 可以代表“看！”的意思，而方括号 ([ ]) 可以让你想到“描述”，圆括号 ( ( ) ) 可以让你想到“URL”。通过这种关联，你可以更容易地记住图片的 Markdown 语法：`![图片描述](图片 URL)。`\r\n### 在这里试一试\r\n![这是一张 500px.com 的风景图片]( http://many-video.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/photos/2023_0322_123418_386ar7z5.png)", "content_rendered": "<h3>刚刚学习了 markdown 的图片语法</h3>\n<h4>关联记忆法：将 Markdown 语法与已知概念进行关联。例如，在 Markdown 语法中，感叹号 (!) 可以代表“看！”的意思，而方括号 ([ ]) 可以让你想到“描述”，圆括号 ( ( ) ) 可以让你想到“URL”。通过这种关联，你可以更容易地记住图片的 Markdown 语法：<code>![图片描述](图片 URL)。</code></h4>\n<h3>在这里试一试</h3>\n<p><img alt=\"这是一张 500px.com 的风景图片\" class=\"embedded_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"http://many-video.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/photos/2023_0322_123418_386ar7z5.png\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1679459863, "replies": 75, "id": 926148}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_large.png?m=1611920927", "name": "games", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_normal.png?m=1611920927", "titl